WEBVTT

01:37.920 --> 01:41.020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.060 --> 01:43.990
[Episode 15]

01:49.780 --> 01:50.479
Serving chopsticks.

01:50.479 --> 01:50.950
Get another pair.

01:50.950 --> 01:53.009
Don't bump into it when turning this.

01:54.070 --> 01:54.729
Over here.

01:55.039 --> 01:55.950
Hurry up.

01:56.400 --> 01:57.430
Put one here,

01:57.560 --> 01:58.280
and put one here.

01:58.280 --> 02:00.340
Don't bump into it when turning this.

02:01.880 --> 02:02.630
[February 5 Wednesday 14:45]

02:02.920 --> 02:05.100
Chef Jia took more than
half the kitchen staff with him.

02:05.100 --> 02:05.830
I need staff.

02:06.550 --> 02:07.470
How many do you need?

02:07.470 --> 02:08.490
I want 3 sous chefs,

02:08.490 --> 02:09.550
and a dessert chef.

02:10.169 --> 02:11.360
I can't give you 3.

02:11.390 --> 02:12.380
I'll give you 1 first.

02:12.380 --> 02:15.380
I'll transfer the rest to you
from other departments.

02:15.550 --> 02:15.990
Okay.

02:16.470 --> 02:17.870
Mr. Ji, Mr. Xue.

02:18.250 --> 02:18.810
What is it?

02:18.810 --> 02:21.280
I just went to Manager Chen of purchasing

02:21.280 --> 02:23.280
to have him sign
the guests' dietary restriction list.

02:23.280 --> 02:25.740
I happened to see him
lock the door and leave,

02:25.840 --> 02:27.570
so I came to ask what is going on.

02:28.190 --> 02:28.710
Got it.

02:29.420 --> 02:30.430
As for people from other departments,

02:30.430 --> 02:31.280
I want Xu Miyu.

02:31.300 --> 02:33.430
You can arrange the rest as you see fit.

02:35.120 --> 02:35.870
Ms. Xu,

02:35.940 --> 02:37.910
our kitchen is understaffed right now.

02:37.910 --> 02:38.840
Are you willing

02:38.840 --> 02:40.680
to stay and help Chef Li?

02:42.800 --> 02:43.450
I am.

02:44.960 --> 02:45.430
Great.

02:45.430 --> 02:46.220
And me.

02:46.680 --> 02:47.480
I can help too.

02:48.070 --> 02:48.770
You?

02:49.190 --> 02:50.280
I can cook.

02:50.560 --> 02:52.400
I made the 8 cold dishes and 8 hot dishes

02:52.400 --> 02:53.840
for our family's New Year's Eve dinner.

02:53.840 --> 02:54.590
Then Chef Li,

02:54.590 --> 02:55.910
you decide this.

02:56.630 --> 02:57.890
Where is the sous chef?

02:58.590 --> 02:59.280
Here.

02:59.750 --> 03:00.470
Come here.

03:03.440 --> 03:04.460
I am Guo Luda.

03:04.560 --> 03:05.750
Okay, Mr. Guo.

03:05.750 --> 03:07.190
Today you are responsible
for reading the orders

03:07.190 --> 03:08.080
and serving the food.

03:08.080 --> 03:09.910
The banquet hall and the Chinese
restaurant must be separated.

03:09.910 --> 03:11.510
You can't make any mistakes.

03:11.910 --> 03:12.560
Okay, no problem.

03:12.560 --> 03:13.240
Okay.

03:13.500 --> 03:14.820
It's 3:10 now.

03:15.800 --> 03:16.530
Let's begin.

03:18.150 --> 03:19.270
Come on, hurry up.

03:21.310 --> 03:22.400
Find someone to open the office.

03:22.400 --> 03:22.930
Okay.

03:40.190 --> 03:40.910
Darn it.

03:41.120 --> 03:42.960
Chen ran off with Jia Shikun.

03:44.590 --> 03:46.280
I never thought about

03:46.280 --> 03:48.880
getting anything
from them in the first place.

03:50.190 --> 03:52.750
But now they've made things look so ugly.

03:52.600 --> 03:55.780
[Staff Personal Health Standard]

03:58.190 --> 04:00.240
The troubles facing the Chinese restaurant

04:00.240 --> 04:02.240
may be worse than I imagined.

04:15.560 --> 04:17.480
Prepare some flour and minced meat for me.

04:17.480 --> 04:18.620
Okay. How much meat?

04:18.950 --> 04:19.560
1.5 kg?

04:19.870 --> 04:20.430
2.5?

04:21.240 --> 04:21.950
2.5 kg.

04:23.190 --> 04:24.510
Then slice some sweet potatoes,

04:24.510 --> 04:25.720
along with perilla leaves and eggplant.

04:25.720 --> 04:26.680
Make all the slices a bit thick.

04:26.680 --> 04:27.510
Hurry up.

04:27.560 --> 04:28.000
Okay.

04:31.120 --> 04:32.190
We're still short-handed.

04:32.190 --> 04:33.790
Find some more people for me.

04:39.830 --> 04:40.560
All washed?

04:41.430 --> 04:43.270
Do you know how to peel tomatoes?

04:43.680 --> 04:44.310
Peel them?

04:44.720 --> 04:45.920
Okay, I'll do it.

04:51.510 --> 04:52.870
I'd better do it.

04:53.190 --> 04:54.290
Didn't she say we're short-handed?

04:54.290 --> 04:55.190
Let me do it.

04:58.240 --> 04:59.500
Why don't you try this?

05:00.430 --> 05:01.190
Okay.

05:02.070 --> 05:05.720
Just score a cross at the top.

05:09.480 --> 05:13.370
Then put it in boiling water.

05:14.610 --> 05:16.150
Then the skin will split open.

05:16.150 --> 05:16.680
Try it.

05:16.700 --> 05:17.330
Okay.

05:32.430 --> 05:33.240
It didn't burn you, did it?

05:33.240 --> 05:33.920
I'm fine.

05:34.270 --> 05:36.600
You have to slide the tomatoes

05:36.600 --> 05:38.040
down the side of the pot.

05:38.210 --> 05:39.430
Don't just drop them in from the top.

05:39.430 --> 05:42.030
Otherwise, the splashing water
will burn you.

05:42.159 --> 05:43.090
Let me try again.

06:10.370 --> 06:11.350
Here it comes.

06:11.870 --> 06:12.930
Careful, it's hot.

06:17.240 --> 06:18.570
Looks and smells great.

06:18.720 --> 06:19.720
How does it taste?

06:20.310 --> 06:21.120
It's time.

06:25.720 --> 06:28.150
Guys, it's 5:00.

06:28.330 --> 06:29.120
Hurry up.

06:29.120 --> 06:31.590
Dinner in the banquet hall
starts promptly at 6:30.

06:31.590 --> 06:33.590
Let's hurry up, guys! Come on!

06:46.060 --> 06:47.590
You'd better go help Mr. Ji.

06:53.870 --> 06:54.510
Mr. Ji.

06:54.810 --> 06:55.909
I'll take over.

06:56.020 --> 06:57.360
You go greet the guests.

07:00.240 --> 07:02.930
Okay, I'll leave the rest to you.

07:03.390 --> 07:04.120
Give it to me.

07:06.780 --> 07:08.070
I put your suit

07:08.070 --> 07:09.040
in the kitchen office.

07:09.040 --> 07:11.040
I was afraid it might get dirty here.

07:12.800 --> 07:13.400
Thank you.

07:23.920 --> 07:24.870
Thank you for coming all this way.

07:24.870 --> 07:25.560
Not at all.

07:25.560 --> 07:27.380
You can go over there first.

07:27.630 --> 07:28.960
Please, right this way.

07:30.830 --> 07:31.600
Kenny.

07:33.000 --> 07:33.810
Marcos.

07:34.680 --> 07:35.430
We meet again.

07:35.430 --> 07:36.220
Yes.

07:36.360 --> 07:37.240
Let me make an introduction.

07:37.240 --> 07:39.680
This is the Commercial Director
of Puqi Group.

07:39.680 --> 07:40.430
Mr. Cheng.

07:40.430 --> 07:41.460
Mr. Cheng, this is

07:41.560 --> 07:43.450
Mr. Ji Feng, General Manager
of Purong Hotel.

07:43.450 --> 07:44.380
Nice to meet you.

07:44.430 --> 07:45.560
Nice to meet you, too, Mr. Cheng.

07:45.560 --> 07:47.000
We have your table ready.

07:48.030 --> 07:49.490
Sorry to keep you waiting.

07:50.520 --> 07:52.350
We've prepared an appetizer for you.

07:50.810 --> 07:53.310
[All staff of Purong Hotel]

07:53.240 --> 07:55.800
I believe it's a dish
you're very familiar with.

07:53.330 --> 07:56.500
[warmly welcome Mr. Marcos]

07:55.800 --> 07:56.430
Thank you.

07:56.520 --> 07:59.060
[We will serve you sincerely]

07:59.870 --> 08:00.720
Okay.

08:01.120 --> 08:04.160
This is a Spanish cold soup.

08:06.040 --> 08:07.570
Enjoy your meal, everyone.

08:18.140 --> 08:18.920
I'm serious.

08:19.600 --> 08:20.730
This tastes exactly

08:20.950 --> 08:23.830
the same
as what I had in Cordoba.

08:24.510 --> 08:25.150
Really?

08:25.180 --> 08:26.180
You should try it.

08:29.750 --> 08:31.040
That's something.

08:31.640 --> 08:32.240
Thank you.

08:32.720 --> 08:33.289
Enjoy.

08:35.960 --> 08:36.600
Not bad.

08:38.789 --> 08:40.590
Next up are the Shanghai dishes.

08:40.840 --> 08:41.510
Come on.

08:43.909 --> 08:44.790
Please enjoy.

08:55.160 --> 08:57.490
This is exactly like
the kind I had as a kid,

08:57.510 --> 08:59.120
deep-fried dough sticks
made from sourdough.

08:59.120 --> 09:00.790
Your hands would be
covered in oil after eating.

09:00.790 --> 09:02.150
It smelt so great.

09:02.600 --> 09:03.840
It's a pity that nowadays,

09:03.840 --> 09:05.270
you can't find
breakfast shops like this anymore.

09:05.270 --> 09:06.120
I see.

09:06.240 --> 09:07.290
That's a pity.

09:08.720 --> 09:10.150
Then we hope you

09:10.150 --> 09:11.940
can come to our hotel
for breakfast more often, Mr. Cheng.

09:11.940 --> 09:12.610
It's a deal.

09:13.510 --> 09:13.910
Mr. Cheng,

09:13.910 --> 09:16.310
is it convenient for me
to add you on WeChat?

09:16.390 --> 09:16.790
No problem.

09:16.790 --> 09:18.120
Come, add her on WeChat.

09:19.150 --> 09:20.150
What do you think?

09:20.150 --> 09:21.030
It's fried quite well.

09:21.030 --> 09:21.550
Just right.

09:21.470 --> 09:22.160
[All staff of Purong Hotel]

09:21.550 --> 09:22.180
What do you think?

09:22.180 --> 09:22.880
[warmly welcome Mr. Marcos]

09:22.390 --> 09:22.840
You can scan my code.

09:22.840 --> 09:23.720
It smells really great.

09:22.900 --> 09:23.590
[We will serve you sincerely]

09:24.960 --> 09:26.030
The taste of childhood.

09:26.030 --> 09:26.730
Right?

09:29.120 --> 09:30.370
Okay, got it.

09:30.740 --> 09:32.430
Are you satisfied with the dishes?

09:32.430 --> 09:33.370
Isn't it greasy?

09:33.440 --> 09:35.080
If you feel it's too greasy,
some soy milk will help.

09:35.080 --> 09:36.150
Enjoy your meal.

09:36.150 --> 09:37.880
It can relieve the greasiness.

09:49.030 --> 09:50.290
Eight-Treasure Duck.

09:50.390 --> 09:51.270
It's done.

09:53.040 --> 09:53.600
[Purong Hotel Chinese Restaurant; Dine-In;
Eight-Treasure Duck]

09:56.030 --> 09:58.430
Poached Shrimp, one, two, three.

09:58.630 --> 10:00.030
Seven plates of Poached Shrimp.

10:00.030 --> 10:00.630
No, eight...

10:00.630 --> 10:01.430
Eight plates.

10:01.630 --> 10:02.850
How many plates exactly?

10:02.850 --> 10:03.630
Don't worry about it.

10:03.630 --> 10:05.200
Start cooking first.
We'll plate whatever we get.

10:05.200 --> 10:06.670
The guest would like to cancel
the Tofu with Crab Roe.

10:06.670 --> 10:07.870
Tofu with Crab Roe...

10:08.030 --> 10:10.030
This has garlic.
The guest wants it remade.

10:10.030 --> 10:11.830
So noisy.
My head’s about to explode.

10:11.830 --> 10:12.930
Put it there first.

10:13.240 --> 10:15.370
And Stir-Fried Shrimp with Rice Wine.

10:15.440 --> 10:16.700
-Is it done?
-Yes. Yes.

10:20.150 --> 10:20.910
Waiter,

10:20.910 --> 10:22.390
when will the dishes
for our table be served?

10:22.390 --> 10:24.000
We've been waiting
for nearly half an hour.

10:24.000 --> 10:24.750
The kitchen is preparing.

10:24.750 --> 10:25.270
It will be served right away.

10:25.270 --> 10:25.870
Please wait a moment.

10:25.870 --> 10:27.150
Hurry up.

10:27.510 --> 10:28.270
Waitor,

10:28.510 --> 10:29.630
we've finished our cold dishes.

10:29.630 --> 10:30.910
When will you serve us the hot dishes?

10:30.910 --> 10:31.390
Right away.

10:31.390 --> 10:32.000
I'll go urge them now.

10:32.000 --> 10:32.750
Hurry up.

10:39.270 --> 10:40.790
Mr. Guo, you go inside and help.

10:40.790 --> 10:41.720
Leave this to me.

10:41.910 --> 10:42.330
Okay.

10:43.630 --> 10:44.630
Get me a fresh one.

10:45.240 --> 10:45.670
Here.

10:52.630 --> 10:54.510
Six portions of Braised Wheat Gluten.

10:54.510 --> 10:55.120
Okay.

11:09.670 --> 11:10.750
Okay, go.

11:11.790 --> 11:12.750
Careful.

11:17.120 --> 11:18.870
Is the Tempura ready?

11:18.870 --> 11:19.960
A bunch of idiots.

11:19.960 --> 11:21.320
Hurry up, bro!

11:23.430 --> 11:24.200
Mr. Ji.

11:28.030 --> 11:28.790
Sorry, Mr. Ji.

11:28.790 --> 11:29.390
I was in such a hurry,

11:29.390 --> 11:30.510
I didn't recognize you.

11:30.510 --> 11:31.640
-It’s okay.
-Sorry.

11:31.670 --> 11:32.320
Mr. Ji,

11:32.510 --> 11:33.630
the large private room
in the Chinese restaurant

11:33.630 --> 11:35.240
just ordered 18 portions
of Hainanese Chicken Rice at once.

11:35.240 --> 11:36.120
The staff were too quick.

11:36.120 --> 11:37.840
They've already served all the chicken rice
meant for the banquet hall.

11:37.840 --> 11:39.790
We might come up short here.

11:40.240 --> 11:42.030
Chef Li, are there any other options?

11:42.030 --> 11:42.960
We can use the cooked rice

11:42.960 --> 11:44.270
to make soy sauce fried rice.

11:44.270 --> 11:45.390
But it's too hard.

11:45.390 --> 11:46.270
It's not suitable for the final dish.

11:46.270 --> 11:47.730
How about making noodles?

11:47.910 --> 11:49.510
I'm afraid it's too late to make it now.

11:49.510 --> 11:50.670
What kind of noodles do you want to make?

11:50.670 --> 11:51.840
The guests have been eating

11:51.840 --> 11:52.910
seafood and red meat all night.

11:52.910 --> 11:54.750
A bowl of plain noodles now

11:54.750 --> 11:56.040
would be refreshing
and cut through the grease.

11:56.040 --> 11:58.030
It's good, but it lacks a gimmick.

11:59.440 --> 12:00.790
We can make plain noodles in chicken soup.

12:00.790 --> 12:02.400
Chicken soup with mature hen
from Southern Anhui.

12:02.400 --> 12:03.150
Since it's to cleanse the palate,

12:03.150 --> 12:04.280
it can't be too rich.

12:06.120 --> 12:07.320
How about Fish Bone Soup
with Bamboo Leaves?

12:07.320 --> 12:08.050
I can make it.

12:08.240 --> 12:08.870
You'll make it.

12:08.870 --> 12:09.240
Okay.

12:09.550 --> 12:10.790
Chef Li, please keep
an eye on things here.

12:10.790 --> 12:11.550
I'll go outside and take a look.

12:11.550 --> 12:11.880
Okay.

12:12.030 --> 12:12.560
Let's go.

13:14.920 --> 13:15.450
Mr. Ji.

13:16.770 --> 13:17.590
Try some.

13:18.630 --> 13:19.270
I don't need this much.

13:19.270 --> 13:20.470
I'll just have a bite.

13:28.440 --> 13:30.150
I haven't tasted it properly yet.

13:30.150 --> 13:31.550
Let me have another bite.

13:40.870 --> 13:41.550
Mr. Ji,

13:41.670 --> 13:43.130
this whole bowl is for you.

13:43.360 --> 13:46.080
You've been too busy to eat all night.

13:46.080 --> 13:48.280
Have some noodles to line your stomach.

13:50.260 --> 13:51.360
Okay, thank you.

14:01.270 --> 14:02.360
Who came up with this terrible idea

14:02.360 --> 14:04.420
to change the menu at the last minute?

14:04.750 --> 14:05.680
What's going on?

14:11.510 --> 14:12.390
Xu Miyu,

14:12.840 --> 14:14.150
why is it you again?

14:14.360 --> 14:15.360
The Hainanese Chicken Rice

14:15.360 --> 14:17.750
is the favorite staple food
of Shenjiang Industrial's boss.

14:17.750 --> 14:18.390
I'm telling you,

14:18.390 --> 14:19.840
this is a business banquet,

14:19.840 --> 14:21.440
not a local feast in your hometown.

14:21.440 --> 14:23.040
Change it back immediately.

14:23.360 --> 14:24.550
Why can any kind of person

14:24.550 --> 14:26.390
boss around in my kitchen now?

14:26.910 --> 14:28.270
Who let this person in?

14:28.360 --> 14:29.440
Kick her out!

14:29.440 --> 14:30.000
Qiaoqi.

14:33.090 --> 14:34.030
Director Lu,

14:36.030 --> 14:37.320
the Hainanese Chicken Rice

14:37.320 --> 14:39.250
was added temporarily at 5:00 p.m.

14:39.550 --> 14:40.870
Why is it no longer available?

14:40.870 --> 14:43.240
It's because the guests in the large
private room of the Chinese restaurant

14:43.240 --> 14:46.580
are business owners from Guangdong's
new energy manufacturing sector.

14:46.580 --> 14:48.580
What do you expect our kitchen to do?

14:50.000 --> 14:51.000
As for this bowl of

14:51.750 --> 14:54.940
plain noodles
in Fish Bone Soup with Bamboo Leaves,

14:55.720 --> 14:57.360
you won't find it

14:57.360 --> 14:58.960
at a typical hometown feast.

14:59.160 --> 15:00.640
The bamboo leaves are from

15:00.670 --> 15:02.480
Mount Emei in Sichuan.

15:02.870 --> 15:06.000
The fish bones come from
Pengze crucian carp in Jiangxi.

15:06.000 --> 15:06.910
And these noodles

15:06.910 --> 15:08.510
are fresh handmade noodles.

15:08.910 --> 15:11.440
Now you know how to
introduce it to the guests, right?

15:11.440 --> 15:14.000
What are these nonsense words
you cobbled together?

15:14.000 --> 15:15.460
Are you trying to bluff me?

15:15.600 --> 15:17.510
I don't care what ingredients you use.

15:17.510 --> 15:18.630
If this noodle dish fails,

15:18.630 --> 15:20.360
will you take responsibility?

15:20.750 --> 15:21.440
I will.

15:27.600 --> 15:28.520
Mr. Ji.

15:29.390 --> 15:30.390
Mr. Ji, I'm sorry.

15:30.560 --> 15:32.600
I was just too anxious.

15:36.510 --> 15:38.360
Director Lu, do me a favor.

15:43.870 --> 15:45.750
Should I take these noodles up?

15:48.550 --> 15:49.670
Put them on the cart.

15:49.670 --> 15:51.730
How could we let you serve the dishes?

16:06.840 --> 16:08.000
Not bad. Pretty good.

16:08.000 --> 16:08.600
Glad you like it.

16:08.600 --> 16:09.330
Pretty good.

16:10.990 --> 16:12.650
Marcos, let me introduce you.

16:14.060 --> 16:16.360
This is the executive chef
in charge of tonight's dinner,

16:16.360 --> 16:17.510
Chef Li Qiaoqi.

16:17.960 --> 16:18.750
Marcos.

16:18.920 --> 16:19.790
Mr. Cheng.

16:20.080 --> 16:20.790
-Hello, Chef Li.
-Hello.

16:20.790 --> 16:22.870
Hello. I didn't expect you to be so young.

16:22.870 --> 16:24.540
Chef, let me tell you,

16:24.960 --> 16:26.160
I am really satisfied

16:26.320 --> 16:27.750
with tonight's dinner.

16:30.360 --> 16:31.600
Mr. Cheng even said

16:31.600 --> 16:32.790
he must see for himself

16:32.790 --> 16:34.390
such an amazing chef like you.

16:34.390 --> 16:35.000
Also,

16:35.000 --> 16:36.150
I want to

16:36.150 --> 16:38.280
express my gratitude to you in person.

16:38.390 --> 16:39.390
Thank you for your hard work.

16:39.390 --> 16:41.510
The praise from Mr. Marcos and Mr. Cheng

16:41.510 --> 16:42.440
is our honor.

16:43.000 --> 16:44.000
Actually, in Purong,

16:44.000 --> 16:45.720
there are many chefs like me.

16:49.000 --> 16:50.000
Thank you all.

16:50.120 --> 16:51.720
Thank you for your hard work.

16:54.990 --> 16:55.720
This lady...

16:56.820 --> 16:58.060
My butler?

17:00.150 --> 17:01.590
Hello, Mr. Marcos.

17:01.910 --> 17:02.550
Actually,

17:02.870 --> 17:03.750
your butler is also

17:03.750 --> 17:05.569
a very excellent chef.

17:05.849 --> 17:08.210
Today's plain noodles are made by her.

17:08.790 --> 17:12.150
I really finished that bowl
of plain noodles.

17:13.240 --> 17:14.550
What a surprise, Ms. Xu.

17:14.550 --> 17:16.810
I didn't expect you
to be such a good cook.

17:17.310 --> 17:17.859
Well,

17:18.400 --> 17:19.400
can I

17:19.510 --> 17:22.400
order the plain noodles now

17:22.400 --> 17:23.930
for my breakfast tomorrow?

17:24.109 --> 17:25.270
My pleasure.

17:25.839 --> 17:27.440
Then I want to order a bowl too.

17:27.440 --> 17:28.790
I will come here specifically tomorrow

17:28.790 --> 17:30.320
to have this for breakfast.

17:30.680 --> 17:31.430
No problem.

17:32.110 --> 17:33.840
Let's add each other on WeChat.

17:34.790 --> 17:35.570
Well,

17:35.640 --> 17:37.440
I think the food here
tastes really good.

17:37.440 --> 17:38.550
The most important thing is the broth.

17:38.550 --> 17:39.830
It's hard to make.

17:39.830 --> 17:41.630
That broth is really delicious.

17:56.440 --> 17:57.640
They are back.

18:06.270 --> 18:07.860
Awesome.

18:15.590 --> 18:16.460
Good job, everyone.

18:16.460 --> 18:17.370
You did great.

18:18.790 --> 18:21.390
We finally got through
this without a hitch.

18:21.830 --> 18:23.510
Even though Chef Jia

18:23.510 --> 18:25.110
disappeared without a word,

18:25.350 --> 18:27.680
our Chinese restaurant won't disappear.

18:29.640 --> 18:30.640
Chef Li Qiaoqi,

18:31.070 --> 18:31.750
starting tomorrow,

18:31.750 --> 18:35.010
you will be the acting
head chef of the Chinese restaurant.

18:44.200 --> 18:45.210
Any objections?

18:45.590 --> 18:46.960
Feel free to raise them

18:46.990 --> 18:48.850
and we can discuss them together.

18:49.200 --> 18:50.060
No objections.

18:55.510 --> 18:57.000
Since there are no objections,

18:57.000 --> 18:58.480
please follow

18:58.640 --> 19:00.920
the new head chef

19:01.590 --> 19:02.590
and work together

19:02.830 --> 19:05.200
to keep our Chinese restaurant running.

19:05.590 --> 19:06.110
Okay?

19:06.110 --> 19:07.350
Okay!

19:16.540 --> 19:18.030
Good. Thanks for your hard work.

19:18.030 --> 19:19.400
Wrap up your work,

19:19.400 --> 19:20.440
and go rest early.

19:20.440 --> 19:21.070
Okay.

19:22.960 --> 19:24.060
Thanks.

19:24.310 --> 19:25.030
Thanks.

19:27.030 --> 19:28.070
I didn't expect this at all.

19:28.070 --> 19:29.310
You are the best.

19:30.070 --> 19:31.400
You must be exhausted today too.

19:31.400 --> 19:32.640
I'm fine.

19:33.160 --> 19:34.440
Thanks for your help.

19:35.590 --> 19:36.750
I have something else to do.

19:36.750 --> 19:37.680
I'll get going.

19:40.440 --> 19:41.030
Qiaoqi.

19:42.350 --> 19:43.010
I made this.

19:43.160 --> 19:43.790
Try it.

19:46.590 --> 19:49.120
Eunuch Xue, are you
bribing the new head chef?

19:49.880 --> 19:51.170
How am I like a eunuch?

19:51.200 --> 19:52.550
What kind of nickname is that?

19:52.550 --> 19:54.350
You're biting the hand that feeds you.

19:54.350 --> 19:55.510
Eat it while it's hot.

19:55.510 --> 19:56.200
Thank you.

19:56.830 --> 19:58.290
I'll get back to work then.

20:01.440 --> 20:04.070
Eunuch Xue? How do I look like a eunuch?

20:04.070 --> 20:04.830
What?

20:06.550 --> 20:08.920
The Chinese restaurant found
a new head chef so quickly?

20:08.920 --> 20:10.510
She was promoted from the original

20:10.510 --> 20:11.310
sous-chefs of the Chinese restaurant.

20:11.310 --> 20:14.440
She was set to become head chef
after tonight's banquet.

20:14.790 --> 20:16.400
Didn't Jia Shikun tell me

20:16.400 --> 20:18.350
that everyone in the Chinese restaurant
except him is useless

20:18.350 --> 20:19.440
and can't accomplish anything?

20:19.440 --> 20:20.030
Then...

20:22.300 --> 20:23.760
What's wrong with Ji Feng?

20:24.200 --> 20:25.400
Is he just grasping at straws?

20:25.400 --> 20:26.350
Or is it that

20:26.920 --> 20:28.980
Jia Shikun is completely lying to me?

20:30.030 --> 20:32.090
That won't do. I have to go take a look.

20:50.960 --> 20:52.290
Isn't this Mr. Duan Jr.?

20:52.550 --> 20:54.850
What brings you down to our kitchen?

20:54.980 --> 20:58.160
So, where's your new head chef?

20:58.160 --> 20:59.620
Why are you looking for me?

21:01.880 --> 21:02.750
It's you?

21:04.350 --> 21:05.510
Can't it be me?

21:05.590 --> 21:06.990
You're on Ji Feng's side?

21:07.640 --> 21:09.840
Whoever promotes me,
I'm on their side.

21:10.550 --> 21:11.480
What do you want?

21:15.280 --> 21:16.880
How much does Ji Feng pay you?

21:16.990 --> 21:18.090
I'll double it.

21:18.270 --> 21:19.130
Come to Kuanli,

21:19.440 --> 21:21.300
and you can still be the head chef.

21:22.350 --> 21:23.550
Why are you laughing?

21:24.310 --> 21:24.990
Nothing.

21:25.160 --> 21:26.680
I just learned for the first time

21:26.680 --> 21:29.460
that your head chefs
at Kuanli come in bulk.

21:30.070 --> 21:31.200
You think I'm lying?

21:32.880 --> 21:34.350
If I'm not mistaken,

21:34.510 --> 21:36.350
Jia Shikun was also lured to Kuanli

21:36.350 --> 21:37.590
by your words.

21:37.960 --> 21:40.750
Mr. Duan Jr., I might lack backbone,

21:40.780 --> 21:43.100
but you don't have
to treat me like a fool.

21:49.510 --> 21:50.750
Don't be ungrateful.

21:54.070 --> 21:55.100
Sorry,

21:55.310 --> 21:56.550
I really plan

21:56.550 --> 21:58.400
to stay in Purong's kitchen.

21:58.590 --> 21:59.920
What can you do about it?

22:03.690 --> 22:05.340
[F&B Department, Li Qiaoqi]

22:04.030 --> 22:05.030
Li Qiaoqi, right?

22:06.790 --> 22:07.920
Let's see

22:07.920 --> 22:09.580
how big a storm you can stir up.

22:09.830 --> 22:10.890
Let's wait and see.

22:11.920 --> 22:13.680
Take care. I won't see you out.

22:40.270 --> 22:42.590
Mr. Yang, may I walk you
through tomorrow's schedule?

22:42.590 --> 22:44.030
Our hotel has prepared...

22:44.030 --> 22:44.830
Wait a minute.

22:49.440 --> 22:50.270
Hello?

22:51.100 --> 22:52.990
Ms. Xu, give me the room card.

22:53.270 --> 22:56.870
-What? What happened to my grandpa?
-I’ll go open the door.

23:10.740 --> 23:12.200
Mr. Yang, are you alright?

23:18.170 --> 23:20.300
My grandpa fell into a coma yesterday.

23:22.110 --> 23:24.710
He woke up today
and couldn't remember anyone.

23:28.110 --> 23:30.350
I want to rest early tonight.

23:31.820 --> 23:33.550
I understand. I'll arrange it.

23:34.590 --> 23:36.110
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

23:38.350 --> 23:40.720
Mr. Yang, the room is ready for you.

23:40.750 --> 23:42.810
I haven't finished what I was saying.

23:43.200 --> 23:44.200
Mr. Yang is tired.

23:44.350 --> 23:45.310
He wants to rest.

23:45.590 --> 23:46.880
I have important matters
to discuss with him.

23:46.880 --> 23:47.400
What do you know?

23:47.400 --> 23:48.680
You can talk to him about it tomorrow.

23:48.680 --> 23:49.920
Whatever it is,

23:50.400 --> 23:51.600
we'll talk tomorrow.

23:52.920 --> 23:53.990
Okay.

23:54.200 --> 23:55.330
I won't disturb you.

23:55.510 --> 23:56.310
Good night.

24:02.880 --> 24:04.080
Good night, Mr. Yang.

24:04.680 --> 24:05.400
Thank you.

24:15.980 --> 24:17.760
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

24:24.350 --> 24:26.680
[Marcos's grandfather attended
the youth architectural design program]

24:26.700 --> 24:29.210
[at Huiwen Yingzao in Shanghai, China.]

24:30.780 --> 24:32.440
[Marcos's grandfather attended
the youth architectural design program]

24:32.460 --> 24:34.200
[at Huiwen Yingzao in Shanghai, China.]

25:02.880 --> 25:04.410
You've worked hard, honey,

25:04.830 --> 25:06.430
especially being pregnant.

25:07.400 --> 25:08.400
Did the contract signing go smoothly?

25:08.400 --> 25:09.590
Not yet,

25:09.920 --> 25:10.880
but soon.

25:11.000 --> 25:13.030
The boss had a great meal tonight.

25:13.310 --> 25:15.030
He said he was going
to eat somewhere else,

25:15.030 --> 25:16.030
but guess what?

25:16.350 --> 25:18.070
He ended up listening to me.

25:18.260 --> 25:19.550
The five-table banquet

25:19.550 --> 25:21.480
has been moved to our Purong Hotel.

25:23.690 --> 25:25.240
You are amazing, baby.

25:26.030 --> 25:27.790
But that Xu Miyu,

25:28.240 --> 25:29.640
showing off everywhere

25:30.110 --> 25:32.110
and going against me in everything.

25:33.070 --> 25:34.310
She's so annoying.

25:36.240 --> 25:37.310
Who are you talking about?

25:37.310 --> 25:38.450
Who else could it be?

25:38.790 --> 25:39.750
Your ex-wife.

25:40.160 --> 25:40.880
If it weren't for her,

25:40.880 --> 25:43.080
I would have signed the contract today.

25:44.070 --> 25:45.400
She was the one who stopped me,

25:45.400 --> 25:47.600
insisting that the boss needed to rest.

25:48.110 --> 25:49.350
Why is she like this?

25:56.350 --> 25:56.920
I think she must

25:56.920 --> 25:58.030
hate me.

25:58.510 --> 26:01.350
She's trying everything
to exact personal revenge.

26:01.350 --> 26:03.350
I can't be bothered to deal with her.

26:03.640 --> 26:06.070
Anyway, I'll go see the boss
first thing tomorrow morning,

26:06.070 --> 26:07.270
to press my advantage

26:07.510 --> 26:09.840
and make sure to get this contract signed.

26:10.270 --> 26:10.590
Otherwise,

26:10.590 --> 26:11.920
all my hard work over the past 2 days

26:11.920 --> 26:13.310
will be in vain.

26:16.200 --> 26:16.800
Right.

26:17.880 --> 26:20.110
You can definitely
get the contract signed.

26:20.110 --> 26:21.170
I have faith in you.

26:23.310 --> 26:23.970
Go to sleep.

26:24.880 --> 26:27.010
I have to work early tomorrow morning.

26:42.350 --> 26:44.110
What's wrong with me like this now?

26:44.110 --> 26:46.170
I make my own money to support myself.

26:46.400 --> 26:49.530
Is it any more shameful
than being your full-time nanny?

27:10.310 --> 27:11.440
Hello, Director Lu.

27:18.550 --> 27:19.880
Mr. Yang's flight has been rescheduled.

27:19.880 --> 27:22.740
We are arranging a car
to take him to the airport now.

27:23.110 --> 27:23.640
Ms. Lu.

27:23.640 --> 27:25.700
Thank you for your warm hospitality.

27:27.640 --> 27:28.350
Mr. Yang.

27:29.070 --> 27:30.550
Regarding the cooperation agreement

27:30.550 --> 27:31.440
we discussed at the last banquet,

27:31.440 --> 27:33.040
have you made a decision yet?

27:33.200 --> 27:35.720
I have an emergency
and need to leave China now.

27:35.720 --> 27:37.720
Let's discuss our cooperation later.

27:37.720 --> 27:39.650
Thank you for your understanding.

27:39.690 --> 27:41.090
Of course, I understand.

27:41.640 --> 27:43.510
I wonder if you could

27:43.750 --> 27:45.880
reach a letter of intent with us first.

27:46.200 --> 27:48.510
Even a verbal agreement would do.

27:48.510 --> 27:50.960
It would show
your recognition of our services.

27:50.960 --> 27:52.960
Purong Hotel has a great reputation.

27:52.960 --> 27:54.110
There's no need to rush.

27:54.110 --> 27:56.440
Besides, long-term cooperation
is not a trifling matter.

27:56.440 --> 27:59.350
I think we should sit down
and talk this through sometime.

27:59.350 --> 28:00.750
When exactly is that?

28:01.680 --> 28:03.110
That depends on you.

28:03.590 --> 28:04.790
If your hotel

28:05.160 --> 28:07.560
can maintain excellent service as always,

28:08.020 --> 28:09.310
then when I'll visit

28:09.470 --> 28:12.370
and whether we cooperate
is just a matter of time.

28:14.110 --> 28:14.750
Yes.

28:18.440 --> 28:20.900
Ms. Lu, are you coming
to the airport with us?

28:21.310 --> 28:22.350
I won't be going.

28:22.350 --> 28:23.610
I have a meeting later,

28:23.750 --> 28:26.150
so I'll leave it to you
to see him off, Ms. Xu.

28:28.800 --> 28:30.260
Have a safe trip, Mr. Yang.

28:30.550 --> 28:32.430
Welcome back to Purong Hotel.

28:32.430 --> 28:33.070
Thank you.

28:48.430 --> 28:49.630
-Please.
-Thank you.

28:54.600 --> 28:55.500
Mr. Marcos,

28:55.520 --> 28:56.850
your flight is delayed.

28:57.230 --> 28:58.010
How long is the delay?

28:58.010 --> 28:59.270
Four hours.

28:59.310 --> 29:00.070
Four ho...

29:02.050 --> 29:04.650
See if there are
any other places you want to go.

29:05.950 --> 29:06.710
Whatever.

29:07.810 --> 29:09.330
Can I arrange it then?

29:16.080 --> 29:18.140
Let's go to East Changzhi Road first.

29:25.720 --> 29:29.380
This is the Huiwen Architectural Design
and Research Institute.

29:30.350 --> 29:31.750
Its predecessor

29:31.770 --> 29:34.330
was Huiwen Yingzao, built in 1942.

29:35.440 --> 29:37.510
At that time, in addition to
producing a large number

29:37.510 --> 29:39.420
of exquisite architectural designs,

29:39.420 --> 29:41.720
a large group of outstanding

29:41.720 --> 29:43.920
foreign design masters also came here.

29:44.920 --> 29:46.000
They set up

29:46.000 --> 29:48.480
a youth architectural design program here,

29:48.680 --> 29:50.880
cultivating a group of

29:50.880 --> 29:53.720
rare and excellent
architectural design talents for China.

29:53.720 --> 29:54.830
This story

29:54.830 --> 29:56.110
is a fine example,

29:56.110 --> 29:59.070
both in terms of cultural exchange

29:59.070 --> 30:00.680
between China and the world

30:00.750 --> 30:02.590
and in the field of architectural design.

30:02.590 --> 30:03.350
These are some photographs

30:03.350 --> 30:05.720
from Huiwen Yingzao,
including a few group photos

30:05.720 --> 30:06.680
from that time.

30:09.810 --> 30:10.640
Ms. Xu,

30:12.720 --> 30:15.000
the one on the far left of the second row

30:15.320 --> 30:16.380
is my grandfather.

30:18.720 --> 30:20.830
If only he were here too.

30:22.110 --> 30:25.180
Do you want to call your grandfather then?

30:31.070 --> 30:32.550
Will he still remember me?

30:32.680 --> 30:34.540
How will you know if you don't try?

30:39.160 --> 30:41.980
Mr. Yang Siyuan, you have a phone call.

30:43.270 --> 30:44.030
Grandpa.

30:44.590 --> 30:46.450
You have the wrong number, child.

30:48.160 --> 30:49.350
I am in China.

30:49.350 --> 30:51.240
In Shanghai, China.

30:51.790 --> 30:52.590
I'm looking at

30:54.690 --> 30:56.400
your pictures when you were young.

30:56.400 --> 30:58.830
At Huiwen Yingzao, see?

31:06.790 --> 31:07.880
This is Wang.

31:09.310 --> 31:10.330
Li.

31:11.440 --> 31:12.690
This is our monitor.

31:15.590 --> 31:16.880
You still remember them?

31:16.880 --> 31:18.440
More than remember,

31:18.550 --> 31:20.270
I miss them to death.

31:20.930 --> 31:22.710
Huiwen Yingzao.

31:23.000 --> 31:24.550
Shanghai, China.

31:24.880 --> 31:26.610
The place where I once studied.

31:26.830 --> 31:27.510
Yes.

31:30.510 --> 31:31.070
Grandpa.

31:34.790 --> 31:35.790
Grandpa, then...

31:37.830 --> 31:38.790
Then I am...

31:39.240 --> 31:39.880
You...

31:40.170 --> 31:41.870
Aren't you my Marcos?

31:42.110 --> 31:42.830
Come here quickly.

31:42.830 --> 31:43.880
I miss you.

31:45.970 --> 31:47.490
I miss you very much too.

31:48.880 --> 31:50.480
My flight arrives tomorrow,

31:50.590 --> 31:52.520
then I will go see you immediately.

31:52.830 --> 31:53.890
Come over quickly.

31:54.310 --> 31:55.310
I'll wait for you.

31:56.310 --> 31:57.310
See you tomorrow.

31:57.350 --> 31:58.280
I'll hang up now.

32:10.070 --> 32:10.880
Time flies,

32:10.880 --> 32:13.590
but beautiful memories last forever.

32:13.920 --> 32:16.950
Let me take a picture
of you with your grandpa's photo.

32:17.110 --> 32:17.920
Can you?

32:20.070 --> 32:20.790
Come.

32:25.350 --> 32:26.750
One, two, three.

32:30.680 --> 32:31.510
Thank you.

32:38.110 --> 32:38.920
Ms. Xu.

32:40.310 --> 32:41.310
Can I have a hug?

32:41.440 --> 32:42.350
Of course.

32:49.310 --> 32:50.070
Thank you.

32:51.880 --> 32:52.750
You know what?

32:54.070 --> 32:54.750
You...

32:57.110 --> 32:58.170
You know what, I...

32:59.410 --> 33:01.310
You are the most considerate
hotel attendant

33:01.310 --> 33:04.070
I have ever met traveling the world.

33:04.680 --> 33:05.830
You make me feel

33:06.830 --> 33:08.510
especially secure.

33:08.590 --> 33:11.310
It feels very much like coming home.

33:12.440 --> 33:13.900
Thank you for saying that.

33:15.160 --> 33:16.090
Then,

33:16.550 --> 33:19.750
you are welcome to visit
Purong Hotel often in the future.

33:19.860 --> 33:21.290
Coming often is a must.

33:22.140 --> 33:24.390
And I will let all my staff

33:24.590 --> 33:25.680
come and

33:25.970 --> 33:27.920
enjoy the service here.

33:27.920 --> 33:30.520
We will definitely
serve you wholeheartedly.

33:31.680 --> 33:32.550
Okay.

33:33.350 --> 33:35.070
It should be about time.

33:35.240 --> 33:36.900
Let me take you to the airport.

33:37.440 --> 33:38.510
Great, let's go.

33:38.720 --> 33:39.720
This way, please.

33:52.810 --> 33:53.990
[Unread]

33:53.990 --> 33:56.820
[Unread]

33:56.950 --> 33:57.820
[Loading]

33:59.530 --> 34:01.740
[From: CBO Marcos Yang]

34:02.510 --> 34:03.160
It's done.

34:03.640 --> 34:04.440
What's done?

34:04.510 --> 34:07.070
Marcos wants to sign
a long-term contract with us.

34:07.070 --> 34:08.760
This is all so sudden.

34:09.710 --> 34:11.440
I heard gossip from the front desk

34:11.440 --> 34:12.440
that he's very hard to deal with.

34:12.440 --> 34:14.070
He seems pleasant on the outside,

34:14.070 --> 34:15.960
but is as solid as a rock on the inside.

34:15.960 --> 34:17.420
I thought we had no chance.

34:18.550 --> 34:19.350
Secretary Wu,

34:19.400 --> 34:21.440
notify the management to hold a meeting

34:21.440 --> 34:22.440
in an hour,

34:22.590 --> 34:25.190
after Director Lu
comes back from the airport.

34:25.350 --> 34:25.830
Okay.

34:36.670 --> 34:37.400
You're here.

34:37.550 --> 34:38.440
Talk to you later.

34:38.440 --> 34:38.960
Okay.

34:52.110 --> 34:54.280
Our hosting of Liberty Group this time

34:54.840 --> 34:55.880
was very successful.

34:55.880 --> 34:57.920
They have verbally promised

34:58.110 --> 34:59.960
a long-term contract with us.

35:00.630 --> 35:02.670
All processes are moving forward.

35:09.880 --> 35:12.190
The sales department has made
such a great contribution this time.

35:12.190 --> 35:13.150
We should thank

35:13.920 --> 35:15.590
Mr. Qian for his strong support.

35:15.590 --> 35:16.920
You are too kind, Mr. Ji.

35:17.440 --> 35:18.880
This time, our sales department

35:18.880 --> 35:19.920
is honored

35:19.920 --> 35:21.050
to fight side by side

35:21.550 --> 35:23.710
with Mr. Ji.

35:32.510 --> 35:34.110
This time, Director Lu

35:34.110 --> 35:34.920
has secured such an important client

35:34.920 --> 35:36.630
for our hotel.

35:36.880 --> 35:38.360
It demonstrated our strength externally

35:38.360 --> 35:40.710
and boosted our morale internally.

35:41.320 --> 35:44.480
Although Director Lu
just got transferred here,

35:45.110 --> 35:47.280
her performance has been outstanding.

35:47.280 --> 35:49.690
After discussing with Mr. Qian,

35:49.880 --> 35:50.710
I announce

35:51.230 --> 35:52.710
that Lu Zhenzhen

35:52.710 --> 35:55.000
is promoted to VIP Account Manager.

36:01.230 --> 36:04.190
Ms. Lu, you'll take the lead

36:04.760 --> 36:06.110
on the follow-up with Liberty Group.

36:06.110 --> 36:06.710
Yes.

36:12.840 --> 36:17.070
[Changzhi Road]

36:21.400 --> 36:23.420
Sir, I'll get off here.

36:37.960 --> 36:39.230
Next is

36:40.440 --> 36:41.640
the HSKP Department.

36:41.840 --> 36:42.550
Well,

36:43.110 --> 36:43.710
Mr. Ji,

36:44.360 --> 36:47.110
our HSKP Department's
performance this time

36:47.110 --> 36:50.110
indeed fell short of
the standard of a five-star hotel.

36:50.110 --> 36:51.920
As the leader in charge,

36:51.940 --> 36:52.730
first of all,

36:53.000 --> 36:54.110
I need to make a self-criticism.

36:54.110 --> 36:55.920
It's my fault for
choosing the wrong person.

36:55.920 --> 36:58.440
The executive floor forewoman Xu Miyu

36:58.440 --> 37:00.440
neglected her duty

37:00.440 --> 37:02.030
while receiving VIP guests.

37:02.030 --> 37:02.920
It almost

37:02.920 --> 37:04.560
caused a major accident,

37:04.760 --> 37:05.800
bringing irreversible losses

37:05.800 --> 37:07.960
to the hotel.

37:08.190 --> 37:08.760
She is...

37:11.400 --> 37:12.100
Xu Miyu.

37:12.510 --> 37:14.070
So you still know how to show up.

37:14.070 --> 37:15.800
You made mistakes at work

37:15.800 --> 37:16.760
and are late for the meeting.

37:16.760 --> 37:18.160
What are you trying to do?

37:19.280 --> 37:21.030
Do you still respect me as your leader?

37:21.030 --> 37:23.590
Do you even care about
the hotel's work discipline?

37:23.590 --> 37:25.440
Do you think just
because you're a forewoman

37:25.440 --> 37:27.150
you can completely disregard us

37:27.150 --> 37:28.320
managers?

37:28.800 --> 37:29.830
No, Mr. Feng.

37:29.860 --> 37:31.710
I was taking a guest to the airport,

37:31.710 --> 37:33.190
and the traffic was
a bit heavy on the way back.

37:33.190 --> 37:34.440
-I'm sorry.
-Look.

37:34.440 --> 37:35.880
Still making excuses.

37:36.300 --> 37:38.360
You blame the traffic
for being late to the meeting.

37:38.360 --> 37:41.440
You forgot the VIP's allergies,

37:41.460 --> 37:43.440
and you blamed others for not telling you.

37:43.440 --> 37:45.760
If all of us were like you,

37:46.000 --> 37:47.190
shirking responsibility

37:47.190 --> 37:48.760
whenever there's a problem,

37:48.760 --> 37:50.290
how would any work get done?

37:50.440 --> 37:51.320
Ms. Xu.

37:51.920 --> 37:55.120
The executive floor
will be ruined by you sooner or later.

37:59.260 --> 38:00.010
Mr. Ji.

38:01.630 --> 38:02.400
I'm sorry.

38:03.400 --> 38:04.570
Our HSKP Department

38:04.760 --> 38:07.230
made such a huge mistake

38:07.230 --> 38:09.090
in this important VIP reception.

38:09.190 --> 38:10.340
I take full responsibility.

38:10.340 --> 38:13.080
I didn't discipline this subordinate well,

38:13.360 --> 38:14.650
and I can't shirk the blame.

38:14.650 --> 38:15.740
Please punish me.

38:20.040 --> 38:21.010
Mr. Feng,

38:21.670 --> 38:23.800
don't be in a hurry to ask for punishment.

38:23.800 --> 38:24.930
Let me finish first.

38:26.320 --> 38:28.670
During the HSKP Department's
VIP reception,

38:28.670 --> 38:31.030
there were some mistakes at first.

38:32.400 --> 38:33.800
But fortunately,

38:33.800 --> 38:36.400
the forewoman and staff
on the executive floor

38:36.400 --> 38:37.890
later

38:37.960 --> 38:39.160
observed carefully,

38:39.320 --> 38:40.590
found the problems in time,

38:40.590 --> 38:42.070
and quickly adjusted themselves

38:42.070 --> 38:43.590
to improve the service quality.

38:43.590 --> 38:45.790
In the end, with high-quality service,

38:45.800 --> 38:48.070
they cooperated with
the F&B and sales departments

38:48.070 --> 38:49.320
and successfully completed

38:49.320 --> 38:50.520
this reception task.

38:50.840 --> 38:52.590
Their performance was commendable.

38:52.590 --> 38:53.070
But as for

38:53.070 --> 38:54.590
the cause of the series of accidents

38:54.590 --> 38:56.150
in the HSKP Department,

38:56.360 --> 38:57.590
investigation shows that

38:57.590 --> 39:00.070
they were caused by a handover accident

39:00.630 --> 39:02.320
during the transfer of documents.

39:02.320 --> 39:03.040
Mr. Feng,

39:04.320 --> 39:06.120
do you have anything to explain?

39:08.800 --> 39:09.570
Well,

39:10.440 --> 39:10.920
well...

39:10.920 --> 39:12.150
As for

39:12.150 --> 39:14.080
the shampoo reselling by our staff

39:14.440 --> 39:16.250
and the linen scandal,

39:16.480 --> 39:17.550
our investigation shows

39:17.550 --> 39:19.110
that you were behind both, Mr. Feng—

39:19.110 --> 39:20.150
stealing from the hotel

39:20.150 --> 39:21.480
and lining your own pockets.

39:21.480 --> 39:23.080
The evidence is conclusive.

39:23.400 --> 39:25.390
In addition, the GM's Office

39:25.590 --> 39:27.320
has recently evaluated the abilities

39:27.320 --> 39:28.850
of all department leaders.

39:29.400 --> 39:31.530
Mr. Feng failed to meet the standards.

39:33.710 --> 39:35.230
Based on the above points

39:35.230 --> 39:37.430
and the hotel management regulations,

39:37.960 --> 39:38.960
I hereby announce

39:39.550 --> 39:42.150
that Mr. Feng is dismissed.

39:46.740 --> 39:48.140
You can't fire me.

39:48.760 --> 39:49.360
Mr. Ji,

39:50.150 --> 39:53.190
Mr. Feng is the head
of HSKP Department after all.

39:53.320 --> 39:54.760
You made the decision

39:55.440 --> 39:57.920
to fire him all by yourself?

39:58.110 --> 39:59.840
Isn't that a bit too hasty?

39:59.840 --> 40:00.440
Exactly.

40:00.810 --> 40:02.480
At the very least, you should

40:02.500 --> 40:04.160
discuss it with Mr. Wei first.

40:04.230 --> 40:05.630
So what you're saying is,

40:05.880 --> 40:07.030
the hotel's general manager

40:07.030 --> 40:09.590
can't make personnel
decisions independently?
